    <item>
      <title>Gitifier 1.1</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <html>
            <head>
              <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8">
              <title>Gitifier 1.1</title>
              <link href="http://github.com/psionides/gitifier/raw/master/Sparkle/appcast.css"
                type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" media="all">
            </head>

            <body>
              <br>
              <h3>Release 1.1</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>showing commit diffs by clicking on growl notifications</li>
                <li>some commits (e.g. from GitHub) can also be opened in the browser</li>
                <li>keep windows on top option (on by default)</li>
                <li>error notifications appear less often</li>
                <li>switched repo/author order in growl header</li>
                <li>fixed some issues with password dialog</li>
                <li>checking if growl is installed at startup</li>
              </ul>
            </body>
          </html>
        ]]>
      </description>
